{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Nous sommes \u00e0 l'heure terrible des cons\u00e9quences.", "start": 0.1, "duration": 5.133}, {"text": "Et ces cons\u00e9quences,", "start": 5.233, "duration": 0.1}, {"text": "elles sont pay\u00e9es par", "start": 5.333, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "le peuple arm\u00e9nien aujourd'hui,", "start": 6.1, "duration": 1.366}, {"text": "qui, dans le Haut-Karabakh,", "start": 7.466, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "est victime d'une op\u00e9ration militaire,", "start": 8.266, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "parce que le silence", "start": 9.933, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "de l'Europe et du monde occidental", "start": 11.7, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "au cours des derniers mois,", "start": 13.0, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "malgr\u00e9 toutes les transgressions", "start": 14.6, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "de l'Azerba\u00efdjan,", "start": 15.9, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "n'a fait qu'inciter Aliyev", "start": 16.5, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "\u00e0 aller encore plus loin.", "start": 17.666, "duration": 1.634}, {"text": "Personne ne peut", "start": 19.3, "duration": 1.066}, {"text": "nier qu'aujourd'hui,", "start": 20.366, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "ce qui est viol\u00e9,", "start": 21.133, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "c'est le droit international", "start": 21.9, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "le plus \u00e9l\u00e9mentaire,", "start": 23.1, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "le droit humanitaire.", "start": 24.133, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "Personne ne peut faire", "start": 25.866, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "comme si l'essentiel", "start": 27.366, "duration": 2.034}, {"text": "n'\u00e9tait pas en jeu.", "start": 29.4, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "Et maintenant,", "start": 31.0, "duration": 0.733}, {"text": "il est temps de sortir", "start": 31.733, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "de cette passivit\u00e9,", "start": 33.4, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "quand l'Azerba\u00efdjan pr\u00e9tend", "start": 34.433, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "mener une op\u00e9ration antiterroriste", "start": 35.533, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "et est en r\u00e9alit\u00e9", "start": 37.933, "duration": 0.733}, {"text": "en train de tuer des enfants,", "start": 38.666, "duration": 1.067}, {"text": "des femmes, des civils innocents.", "start": 39.733, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "Il est absolument n\u00e9cessaire", "start": 42.0, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "que nous passions", "start": 43.5, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "des condamnations,", "start": 44.1, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "unanimes ici, et c'est tant mieux,", "start": 45.1, "duration": 1.666}, {"text": "que nous passions", "start": 46.766, "duration": 0.534}, {"text": "des condamnations \u00e0 l'action.", "start": 47.3, "duration": 1.366}, {"text": "Il faut des sanctions", "start": 48.666, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "contre le r\u00e9gime d'Aliyev.", "start": 50.333, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Pas dans une semaine,", "start": 52.333, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "pas dans quelques jours.", "start": 54.066, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "Maintenant,", "start": 54.933, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "dans les heures qui viennent.", "start": 55.433, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "Il faut d\u00e9noncer le contrat gazier", "start": 56.266, "duration": 2.867}, {"text": "honteux qui nous lie", "start": 59.2, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "\u00e0 l'Azerba\u00efdjan.", "start": 60.8, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "Pas dans quelques jours.", "start": 61.833, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "Maintenant.", "start": 63.366, "duration": 0.634}, {"text": "Et cela seul", "start": 64.0, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "peut emp\u00eacher", "start": 65.3, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "que le pire se pr\u00e9sente \u00e0 nous.", "start": 65.9, "duration": 2.266}, {"text": "Car le pire, c'est", "start": 68.166, "duration": 1.867}, {"text": "l'\u00e9puration ethnique", "start": 70.033, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "qu\u2019Aliyev veut organiser,", "start": 71.4, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "qu'il a dit vouloir organiser.", "start": 72.7, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "Chers coll\u00e8gues, l'Union europ\u00e9enne est n\u00e9e", "start": 75.966, "duration": 3.134}, {"text": "sur l'exp\u00e9rience d'un g\u00e9nocide.", "start": 79.3, "duration": 3.766}, {"text": "Le peuple arm\u00e9nien a d\u00e9j\u00e0", "start": 83.133, "duration": 2.067}, {"text": "subi un g\u00e9nocide.", "start": 85.2, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "C'\u00e9tait en 1915", "start": 87.3, "duration": 1.833}, {"text": "et aujourd'hui,", "start": 89.133, "duration": 0.567}, {"text": "ceux qui sont", "start": 89.7, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "en train de s'attaquer", "start": 90.3, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "au Haut-Karabakh", "start": 91.5, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "ne m\u00e8nent pas", "start": 92.4, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "seulement une guerre territoriale :", "start": 93.033, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "ils attaquent un peuple", "start": 94.7, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "qu'ils veulent faire dispara\u00eetre,", "start": 95.833, "duration": 2.167}, {"text": "qu'ils veulent rayer de l'histoire. Et pourquoi ?", "start": 98.0, "duration": 2.166}, {"text": "Parce que ce peuple est li\u00e9", "start": 100.166, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "\u00e0 la civilisation europ\u00e9enne,", "start": 101.866, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "par son h\u00e9ritage, par sa culture.", "start": 103.566, "duration": 2.167}, {"text": "Est-ce que nous allons", "start": 105.733, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "rester silencieux ?", "start": 106.433, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "Est-ce que nous nous contenterons", "start": 107.733, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "de grandes d\u00e9clarations ?", "start": 108.6, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "Est-ce que nous allons voir,", "start": 110.4, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "\u00e0 nouveau,", "start": 111.1, "duration": 0.366}, {"text": "le Conseil et la Commission", "start": 111.466, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "poursuivre une forme d'aveuglement volontaire,", "start": 113.033, "duration": 2.033}, {"text": "mettre les deux parties", "start": 115.066, "duration": 2.4}, {"text": "sur le m\u00eame plan ?", "start": 117.466, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "Si nous continuons", "start": 118.8, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "ainsi, chers coll\u00e8gues,", "start": 119.8, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "nous serons responsables", "start": 120.666, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "devant l'histoire", "start": 121.533, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "de ce que nous aurons", "start": 122.866, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "laiss\u00e9 commettre.", "start": 123.833, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "Et ce sera la trahison", "start": 125.033, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "la plus grave que l'Europe", "start": 126.366, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "puisse faire contre elle-m\u00eame.", "start": 127.233, "duration": 0.9}]}